nodes.text: A male Humanoid customs officer was responsible for overseeing Docking Bay 94 in 0 ABY. He accepted a modest bribe of one hundred credits from the crew of the Alabak's Gold, an Alliance to Restore the Republic ship.
This officer is visually similar to the non-canon character Skreen, the technical director of the Manifold Mollusk Matrix and Matrimony Association from Lusaanda.
